\,32\,
5^2=-7\;\;,\;\;5^3=-35=-3\;\;,\;5^6=(5^3)^2=9\;\;,\;5^8=5^6\cdot 5^2=9\cdot (-7)=-63=1
\Longrightarrow 5^8=1\Longrightarrow ord_{32}(5)=8
(-1)^2=1\Longrightarrow ord_{32}(-1)=2
\,\langle 5\rangle\cap\langle -1\rangle=\{1\}\,
